PRELIMINARY EARTHQUAKE PARAMETERS
---------------------------------
 
  * MAGNITUDE      6.8
  * ORIGIN TIME    0000 UTC MAY 23 2015
  * COORDINATES    11.1 SOUTH  163.4 EAST
  * DEPTH          33 KM / 20 MILES
  * LOCATION       SANTA CRUZ ISLANDS REGION
 

EVALUATION
----------
 
  * AN EARTHQUAKE WITH A PRELIMINARY MAGNITUDE OF 6.8 OCCURRED IN
    THE SANTA CRUZ ISLANDS REGION AT 0000 UTC ON SATURDAY MAY 23
    2015.
 
  * BASED ON ALL AVAILABLE DATA... THERE IS NO TSUNAMI THREAT
    FROM THIS EARTHQUAKE.
 

RECOMMENDED ACTIONS
-------------------
 
  * NO ACTION IS REQUIRED.
 

NEXT UPDATE AND ADDITIONAL INFORMATION
--------------------------------------
 
  * THIS WILL BE THE ONLY STATEMENT ISSUED FOR THIS EVENT UNLESS
